Step 4 Some infected individuals recover: The average time to recover from COVID-19 has been computed to be between 12 and 15 days after which the infected individuals move to the recovered group. The average recovery rate \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
