				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$m^I=5.5$$\end{document}mI=5.5, compared to that of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
