				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$m^I=3$$\end{document}mI=3 for faculty/staff. The numbers are chosen such that the average \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
