				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\{90\%, 80\%, 70\%, 60\%\}$$\end{document}{90%,80%,70%,60%} with varying degrees of time delays between testing and reporting of test results. All experiments for this study utilized \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
